  <name>ctail</name>
  <summary>Cross-platform log tail viewer with regex highlighting</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      ctail (color tail) is a desktop log file viewer that lets you tail files in real-time
      with customizable regex-based highlighting. It supports multiple tabs, drag-and-drop
      reordering, and over 20 built-in color themes.
    </p>
    <p>Features include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Real-time log file tailing with auto-scroll</li>
      <li>Regex-based highlighting with line and match modes</li>
      <li>21 built-in themes (dark and light variants)</li>
      <li>Custom theme support via JSON files</li>
      <li>Multiple tabs with drag-and-drop reordering</li>
      <li>Search and filter within log output</li>
      <li>Configurable rule profiles</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  <launchable type="desktop-id">ctail.desktop</launchable>
